high_descs: Turn around, walk a few steps, then turn right and walk over to the bathroom sinks.
Open the left cabinet under the right sink and take out the red rag that is inside.
Move over to stand directly in front of the right hand sink.
Put the red rag in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a rag from a cabinet to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to the sink on the right.
Open the second cabinet from the right under the sink and get the red rag.
Walk to the front of the sink on the right.
Put the red rag in the right sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put the red rag under the sink into the sink basin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter and look down at the lower cabinets.
Open the second cabinet door from the right and take out the red rag, then close the door.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the red rag in the rightmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Move a red rag into a sink.
